Class MapSpecification<I,O,R>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.google.appengine.tools.mapreduce.MapSpecification<I,O,R>
  • Type Parameters:
    I - type of input values
    O - type of output values
    R - type of result returned by the Output
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public final class MapSpecification<I,O,R>
extends java.lang.Object
    Specification for a map-only job. The values here affect what computation is performed in the Map job and its side-effects, but not how it is executed; see MapSettings for that.
